<plot>Munir goes on a vacation in a holiday resort with his two bodyguards. Munis is famous for his affairs with women. There he meets Can, a very emancipated young girl. They fall in love but they are from very different cultures. While Munir is a very traditional man, Can is very modern with European values. Can's family don't like Munir much. Moreover, Munir's ex-girlfriend also turns up. Munir's macho behavior eventually bothers Can and they separate. But Munir is already after a new catch..</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?023452</url></doc>
